snippet.title: (OLD Demo Trailer) The Tale of Two Nekos - Dante's Tale Preview
snippet.description:
(OLD Demo Trailer) The Tale of Two Nekos - Dante's Tale Preview 

Here is a Demo for Dante's Tale that is out now. Keep in mind that this Demo including the final game will be only exclusive to PCs which are Windows, and Linux until I figure out how to port the game to Android

REMINDER: some dialogue/Visuals/and or Gameplay in this Game is not final and is subject to change in the Final Game.
